<!-- About Section -->
<section id="about" class="container content-section text-center">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
            <h2>About Datavis</h2>
            <p>Datavis is a web application that manipulates documents based on data. So far, the technology used are <a href="http://rubyonrails.org/">Ruby on Rails</a> and soon, <a href="https://d3js.org/">D3</a> and <a href="https://dc-js.github.io/dc.js/">dc.js</a>. This includes, of course, the ever essential HTML, SVG, JS, JQuery and CSS.</p>
            <p>Most of the code are available at my <a href="https://github.com/emesc">Github</a> page. I learnt from people who are generous to share their knowledge for free. To pay it forward, should you find the code interesting, feel free to use it for any rightful purpose.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

